      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:6:1",
      "text": [
        " يُضْرَبُ الرَّجُلُ الْحَدَّ قَائِماً وَ الْمَرْأَةُ قَاعِدَةً وَ يُضْرَبُ كُلُّ عُضْوٍ وَ يُتْرَكُ الرَّأْسُ وَ الْمَذَاكِيرُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, form Ali Bin Al Hakam, from Aban, from Zurara, ",
          "Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The man would be whipped by the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) while standing, and the woman whilst seated, and every body part can be whipped except for the head and the sexual parts’."
        ]
      }
